gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 130, Wizards 125
gameRecap.excerpt: Paolo Banchero's 28 points, 13 rebounds and seven assists lead the Magic as they defeated the Wizards, 130-125.  Franz Wagner added 31 points, seven rebounds and eight assists in the victory, while Kyle Kuzma tallied 27 points and six rebounds for the Wizards in the losing effort.  The Magic have won their 9th consecutive game and improve to 14-5 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 3-16.
